name: Japanese samurai robot
description:
One of the most unique things in Japan is the existence of a Samurai, or a swordsman who is still present in the Land of Sakura. One of the sword techniques used by samurai is iaijyutsu, which has been around for hundreds of years. If previously iaijyutsu could only be done by swordsmen, now this ancient swordsmanship can be demonstrated by a robot.

2000x2000 pixel, format mp4.
